Package: tceper
Type: Package
Title: Access to Open Data from the Pernambuco State Court of Accounts (TCE-PE)
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
            person("Andre", "Leite", email = "leite@castlab.org", role = c("aut", "cre")),
            person("Hugo", "Vaconcelos", email = "hugo.vasconcelos@ufpe.br", role = "aut"),
            person("Diogo", "Bezerra", email = "diogo.bezerra@ufpe.br", role = "aut"))
Description: Provides functions to access, download, and process open datasets published by the Pernambuco State Court of Accounts (TCE-PE), through its official Open Data portal. The datasets include information on bids, contracts, expenses, agreements, and other public data.
